{"tid":2108029,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"彭博：英擬分兩階段禁華為參與通訊網絡建設","createTime":"2020-07-14T09:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T09:26:19.000Z","uid":115608,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8318adfd8111cc12aa64e19cf175b161c1dacda0","tid":2108029,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:04:36.000Z","msg":"彭博：英擬分兩階段禁華為參與通訊網絡建設<br />\n4小時前<br />\n彭博：英擬分兩階段禁華為參與通訊網絡建設<br />\n【Now新聞台】彭博社報道，英國政府計劃分兩階段，禁止中國電訊設備商華為參與未來通訊網絡建設，保障通訊關鍵系統免受安全威脅。<br />\n<br />\n彭博引述知情人士指，計劃的第一階段要求所有英國電訊營運商到年底，就不能在5G網絡中增添華為的零件，第二階段則是在2027年前，將所有華為設備從現有5G網絡中移除。<br />\n<br />\n首相約翰遜擔任主席的英國國家安全委員會稍後會開會，討論是否將華為排除出5G網絡建設。外界估計，英國很大可能這樣做，焦點是如何執行有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n英國電訊早前警告，如果急於將華為排除在5G網絡外，可能會令服務中斷。中國駐英大使劉曉明就警告排除華為將損害英國形象，英國需要承擔後果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397893&amp;fbclid=IwAR0dNwesuVcBezU0DTH5MGyWKwutKSLagLvlFKT7sAeoGyocZOI4VKhlRUc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397893%26fbclid%3DIwAR0dNwesuVcBezU0DTH5MGyWKwutKSLagLvlFKT7sAeoGyocZOI4VKhlRUc&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuNlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=efe76da0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397893%26fbclid%3DIwAR0dNwesuVcBezU0DTH5MGyWKwutKSLagLvlFKT7sAeoGyocZOI4VKhlRUc&h=fdca3c0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397893&amp;fbclid=IwAR0dNwesuVcBezU0DTH5MGyWKwutKSLagLvlFKT7sAeoGyocZOI4VKhlRUc</a><br />\n2020年1月30日 08:03"},{"pid":"867a99407c4f1ed9db7364555d8e2c20db19b31c","tid":2108029,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國武漢科技專家：英國不會棄用華為<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2107726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2107726</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb170dcb20510ba529ff153a3a30e53688ba1da9","tid":2108029,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}